INSERT INTO youtube_channels (
    youtube_channel_id,
    title,
    description,
    youtube_created_at,
    views,
    subscribers,
    videos,
    uploads_playlist,
    country
)
VALUES (
    '${youtube_id}', 
    '${title}', 
    '${description}', 
    '${youtube_created_at}', 
    ${views}, 
    ${subscribers}, 
    ${videos}, 
    '${uploads_playlist}', 
    '${country}'
);
